OL,3,CConvent 'in shock' by the death of a
OL,4,Cnun who was hit by a car
OL,6,FA convent has been left in shock by
OL,7,Fthe death of a nun who was hit by a
OL,8,Fcar in South Wales.
OL,10,FSister Genevieve, 87, previously
OL,11,Fcalled Anne Clanchy, died after the
OL,12,Fincident in Stow Park Avenue, Newport,
OL,13,Fin February.
OL,15,FShe was a sister of St Joseph of
OL,16,FAnnecy for 67 years and has been
OL,17,Fdescribed as having shown a "great
OL,18,Fkindness" to everyone she met.
OL,26,@yD@]OUzD@IO]
