OL,3,CConvent 'in shock' by the death of a
OL,4,Cnun who was hit by a car
OL,6,FIn a tribute issued by Gwent Police,
OL,7,Fher fellow sisters said: "She taught
OL,8,Fin various schools in the English
OL,9,Fprovince, spending many years as head
OL,10,Fof St Winifred's School, Lee, in south
OL,11,FLondon.
OL,13,F"In retirement, Sister Genevieve
OL,14,Freturned to her home area of Chatham
OL,15,Fin Kent and later moved to Devizes in
OL,16,FWiltshire.
OL,18,F"There she enjoyed being part of so
OL,19,Fmany parish activities, making many
OL,20,Ffriends.
OL,26,@oD@ZOUuD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/4
