OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1776003065
OL,3,CConvent 'in shock' by the death of a
OL,4,Cnun who was hit by a car
OL,6,F"In recent years she had been living
OL,7,Fin Newport and continued to reach out
OL,8,Fto others through the local groups
OL,9,Fthat she joined.
OL,11,F"Sister Genevieve's sudden death is a
OL,12,Fshock to the sisters and all those who
OL,13,Fknew her.
OL,15,F"She will be remembered for her great
OL,16,Fkindness to everyone that she met, her
OL,17,Finterest in them and their lives, her
OL,18,Flove of life and her quiet, deep
OL,19,Ffaith."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUwD@AOU{D@GO]
