PN,46404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1776003065
OL,3,CConvent 'in shock' by the death of a
OL,4,Cnun who was hit by a car
OL,6,FOfficers from Gwent Police were called
OL,7,Fto a crash involving a pedestrian and
OL,8,Fa car in Stow Park Avenue at around
OL,9,F3.55pm on February 24.
OL,11,FThe pedestrian, Sister Genevieve, was
OL,12,Ftaken to hospital but was later
OL,13,Fpronounced dead.
